### Catching All byLLM Errors

```jac
import from jaclang.byllm.lib { ByLLMError }

with entry {
    try {
        result = my_llm_function(input);
    } except ByLLMError as e {
        print(f"byLLM error: {e}");
        # Fallback logic
    }
}
